001package eu.righettod;
002
003/**
004 * Enumeration used by the method <code>SecurityUtils.applyJWTExtraValidation()</code> to define the type of token.
005 */
006public enum TokenType {
007
008    /**
009     * Access token.
010     *
011     * @see "https://auth0.com/docs/secure/tokens/access-tokens"
012     */
013    ACCESS,
014
015    /**
016     * ID token.
017     *
018     * @see "https://auth0.com/docs/secure/tokens/id-tokens"
019     */
020    ID,
021
022    /**
023     * Refresh token.
024     *
025     * @see "https://auth0.com/docs/secure/tokens/refresh-tokens"
026     */
027    REFRESH
028}
